snippet.title: Bugs Must Die The Final Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Pick your vehicle, arm it with Jackal Rockets and get out there to slay some alien bugs!

The final demo is available on the Bugs Must Die Steam store.
Link: http://bit.ly/2DdMaVS

We would love for you to check it out, and if possible share it with your audience and add this game to your wishlists on Steam. 

Thanks

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Follow us on Twitter:  @dgGamesWorkshop
Here is our website: https://dggamesworkshop.com/

Enjoy the game and
